    <string name="dialog_about_title">About Lexica</string>
    <string name="dialog_about_content">
	Touch the screen and move your finger to adjacent squares to spell words.
	You have three minutes to find as many words as possible.

	\n\nScoring:
	\nOn 4x4 boards, words must be at least three letters long.  On 5x5 boards,
	words must be at least four letters long.
	Words that have three or four letters are worth one point.  Longer words
	are worth more points.  Proper nouns are not counted.\n\n
	</string>
